==Russian==

===Indefinite pronoun===
'''что-нибудь''' (štó-nibud’)
:'''N.B.''' &mdash; the particle [[-нибудь]] imparts a sense of indefiniteness similar to English [[any]]. The forms of '''что-нибудь''' are usually associated with questions and negatives (like [[anything]]), while [[что-то]] is associated with affirmatives (like [[something]]).

# [[anything]]
#:*{{RUchar|[[видеть|Ви́дите]] [[ли]] [[вы]] что́-нибудь?}} — ''Do you see anything?''
#:*{{RUchar|Я [[видеть|ви́жу]] [[что-то|что́-то]]!}} — ''I see something!''

